article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-robotaxi-business-outlook-analysis-stats-stock-share-price-musk-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772707201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8aec9fd4fbd083f298b5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-robotaxi-business-outlook-analysis-stats-stock-share-price-musk-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20research%20from%20Bank%20of%20America%20says%20robotaxis%20now%20account%20for%20more%20than%20half%20the%20company's%20valuation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jciolli%40businessinsider.com%20(Joe%20Ciolli)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-robotaxi-business-outlook-analysis-stats-stock-share-price-musk-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Nobel%20economist%20Paul%20Krugman%20says%20the%20Iran%20war%20could%20be%20the%20'straw%20that%20breaks%20the%20camel's%20back'%20for%20a%20fragile%20US%20economy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Economist%20Paul%20Krugman%20laying%20out%20some%20predictions%20while%20speaking%20at%20an%20event.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a59ba0fd4fbd083f29528f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222813%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESTR%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US-Iran%20war%20has%20sparked%20major%20volatility%20in%20financial%20markets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEconomist%20Paul%20Krugman%20thinks%20the%20war%20could%20have%20significant%20consequences%20for%20the%20US%20economy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20added%20a%20fresh%20level%20of%20massive%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20Krugman%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Iran%20war%20upended%20markets%20this%20week%2C%20and%20economist%20Paul%20Krugman%20thinks%20the%20effects%20could%20ultimately%20be%20much%20more%20far-reaching.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Nobel%20Prize%20winner%20hasn't%20been%20too%20optimistic%20about%20the%20US%20economy%20recently%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20impacts%20he%20sees%20from%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20tariffs.%20Yet%2C%20as%20the%20military%20conflict%20escalates%2C%20he%20sees%20severe%20consequences%20looming%20for%20the%20US%20economy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrugman%20highlighted%20several%20pressing%20factors%20that%20have%20kept%20uncertainty%20high%20in%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpaulkrugman.substack.com%2Fp%2Freality-sets-in-on-trumps-new-war%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESubstack%20post%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20laid%20out%20why%20the%20war%20may%20be%20accelerating%20the%20economy's%20decline.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20many%20stresses%20on%20our%20economy%2C%20and%20this%20could%20be%20the%20straw%20that%20breaks%20the%20camel's%20back%20%E2%80%94%20a%20straw%20that%20becomes%20heavier%20the%20longer%20the%20war%20goes%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Krugman's%20view%2C%20the%20chances%20appear%20increasingly%20slim%20that%20the%20conflict%20will%20be%20resolved%20quickly.%20He%20thinks%20the%20high%20uncertainty%20that%20has%20pushed%20markets%20lower%20is%20likely%20to%20persist%20as%20the%20Trump%20administration%20hasn't%20offered%20a%20clear%20plan%20or%20a%20timeline%20for%20how%20long%20they%20see%20the%20war%20going%20on.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrugman%20sees%20the%20possibility%20that%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%2C%20a%20key%20global%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-us-oil-price-stock-market-energy-iran-commoditiy-war-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eoil%20shipping%20route%3C%2Fa%3E%20controlled%20primarily%20by%20Iran%2C%20could%20remain%20closed%20for%20weeks%20as%20the%20conflict%20drags%20on%2C%20keeping%20oil%20prices%20elevated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20economist%20said%20the%20effects%20of%20higher%20oil%20prices%20and%20an%20expensive%20war%20on%20top%20of%20existing%20economic%20strain%20will%20make%20for%20a%20dangerous%20economic%20scenario.%20He%20flagged%20AI%20an%20one%20such%20risk%20already%20percolating%20through%20the%20system%20as%20markets%20fret%20over%20a%20new%20war%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20widespread%20concerns%20about%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20both%20as%20a%20bubble%20that%20might%20burst%20and%20as%20a%20force%20driving%20job%20losses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20many%20people%2C%20myself%20included%2C%20are%20worried%20about%20financial%20stability%3A%20In%20many%20ways%20we%20have%20recreated%20the%20%26quot%3Bshadow%20banking%26quot%3B%20risks%20that%20made%20the%202008%20crisis%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKrugman%20highlighted%20other%20economic%20concerns%2C%20such%20as%20the%20negative%20impact%20of%20tariffs%20and%20restrictive%20immigration%20policy%2C%20as%20major%20economic%20stress%20points.%20He%20argument%20is%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20fellow%20economist%20Mark%20Zandi%2C%20who%20named%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecession-prediction-us-economy-mark-zandi-tariffs-immigration-trump-policy-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20same%20factors%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20having%20the%20potential%20to%20push%20the%20US%20into%20a%20recession.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20added%20a%20fresh%20level%20of%20massive%20uncertainty%2C%26quot%3B%20Krugman%20said.%20%26quot%3BBear%20in%20mind%20that%20this%20isn't%20even%20a%20war%20of%20choice%3B%20it's%20a%20war%20of%20whim%2C%20marked%20by%20a%20near-total%20lack%20of%20planning.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaul-krugman-iran-conflict-stock-market-economic-outlook-oil-price-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3