d-ed3cff6bf876.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcj4zze5lzjpo%232%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Iranians%20are%20coping%20with%20daily%20strikes%2C%20internet%20blackouts%2C%20and%20security%20crackdowns%20-%20all%20while%20trying%20to%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20loved%20ones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcj4zze5lzjpo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Midlife%20isn't%20a%20crisis%20anymore.%20It's%20a%20career%20rebrand.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiara%20Neal%2C%20Danielle%20Scott%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a87701fd4fbd083f298457%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EElder%20millennials%20are%20turning%2040%2C%20and%20many%20are%20rethinking%20the%20trajectory%20of%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmbitious%20professionals%20are%20using%20the%20moment%20as%20the%20ultimate%20rebrand%20%E2%80%94%20either%20switching%20jobs%20or%20starting%20companies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20expert%20said%20a%20career%20pivot%20is%20often%20not%20about%20boredom%2C%20it%20goes%20much%20deeper%20than%20that.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20working%20in%20TV%2C%20Tiara%20Neal%20felt%20compelled%20to%20change%20the%20channel.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20terrified%20to%20walk%20away%20from%20television%2C%26quot%3B%20Neal%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20went%20to%20school%20for%20it%3B%20it%20was%20all%20I%20had%20ever%20known%2C%20and%20I%20had%20built%20my%20entire%20identity%20around%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeal%20spent%20years%20working%20in%20production%20for%20networks%20like%20BET%20and%20Warner%20Bros.%20Discovery%20before%20a%20health%20crisis%20made%20her%20reexamine%20her%20career.%20Diagnosed%20with%20stage%20one%20breast%20cancer%20at%2034%2C%20she%20learned%20during%20treatment%20to%20navigate%20a%20complex%20medical%20system%2C%20ask%20harder%20questions%2C%20seek%20second%20opinions%2C%20and%20demand%20to%20be%20heard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225828%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiara%20Neal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a877531fb3fcb42648e977%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224371%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20then%20that%20Neal%20was%20introduced%20to%20Bexa%2C%20a%20health-tech%20company%20dedicated%20to%20advancing%20equitable%20early%20breast%20cancer%20detection%20for%20women%20and%20people%20of%20color.%20She%20quickly%20realized%20that%20the%20work%20aligned%20with%20the%20purpose%20that%20had%20been%20on%20her%20heart%20since%20being%20diagnosed%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20with%20great%20insurance%2C%20I%20realized%20how%20easily%20women%20could%20be%20dismissed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20reflected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20shy%20of%20her%2040th%20birthday%2C%20Neal%20left%20television%20altogether%20in%202023%20and%20became%20the%20founding%20executive%20director%20of%20Bexa%20Equity%20Alliance%2C%20the%20company's%20nonprofit%20arm.%20Neal%20now%20leads%20a%20team%20that%20does%20outreach%20to%20help%20close%20the%20detection%20gap%20in%20underserved%20communities.%20In%202025%2C%20for%20example%2C%20Bexa%20partnered%20with%20the%20Essence%20Festival%20of%20Culture%20in%20New%20Orleans%2C%20where%20it%20cohosted%20a%20%26quot%3BWe%20Love%20Us%26quot%3B%20Community%20Day%20to%20provide%20essential%20services%20to%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224317%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tiara%20Neal%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8776efd4fbd083f298467%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225756%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20funny%20because%20I%20never%20imagined%20television%20would%20prepare%20me%20for%20this%2C%20but%20being%20able%20to%20show%20up%20at%20music%20festivals%2C%20conferences%2C%20and%20major%20cultural%20events%2C%20places%20I%20used%20to%20work%20behind%20the%20scenes%2C%20has%20become%20the%20perfect%20bridge%2C%26quot%3B%20Neal%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20meeting%20women%20where%20they%20are.%20We're%20providing%20breast%20exams%20at%20concerts%2C%20at%20large%20gatherings.%20Entertainment%20became%20the%20gateway%20to%20make%20early%20detection%20feel%20approachable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2250403827-fb86-4630-a498-b782ba679934%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20midlife%20crisis%20is%20getting%20a%20rebrand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20treating%20her%20pivot%20as%20a%20midlife%20crisis%2C%20Neal%2C%20now%2040%2C%20said%20she%20sees%20her%20pivot%20as%20a%20rebrand.%20She%20isn't%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20millennials%2C%20turning%2040%20looks%20different%20from%20how%20it%20did%20for%20previous%20generations.%20They've%20spent%20decades%20expertly%20ticking%20off%20the%20boxes%3A%20degrees%2C%20careers%2C%20kids%2C%20mortgages.%20Somewhere%20around%20the%20milestone%20birthday%2C%20the%20life%20they%20may%20have%20worked%20hard%20to%20have%2020%20years%20ago%20doesn't%20quite%20match%20the%20person%20they've%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EForty%20has%20become%20the%20new%20launchpad%20%E2%80%94%20the%20moment%20when%20starting%20over%20feels%20not%20only%20possible%2C%20but%20necessary.%20The%20shift%20is%20both%20structural%20and%20psychological.%20Elder%20millennials%20came%20of%20age%20during%20recessions%2C%20mass%20layoffs%2C%20and%20a%20pandemic%20that%20upended%20entire%20industries%2C%20making%20the%20idea%20of%20career%20stability%20fragile.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20they're%20entering%20midlife%20with%20something%20they%20didn't%20have%20in%20their%2020s%3A%20experience%2C%20credibility%2C%20leverage%2C%20and%20a%20clearer%20sense%20of%20what%20they%20truly%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20most%20recognizable%20second%20acts%20began%20after%2040%3A%20Jan%20Koum%20cofounded%20WhatsApp%20at%2042.%20Julia%20Child%20debuted%20her%20famous%20book%20%26quot%3BMastering%20the%20Art%20of%20French%20Cooking%26quot%3B%20at%2049%2C%20and%20Vera%20Wang%20left%20a%20stable%20editorial%20career%20at%2040%20to%20turn%20her%20name%20into%20an%20eponymous%20fashion%20label.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20data%20suggests%20a%20similar%20pattern%3A%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmitsloan.mit.edu%2Ffaculty%2Fdirectory%2Fpierre-azoulay%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20Pierre%20Azoulay%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20the%20average%20age%20of%20successful%20business%20founders%20is%20around%2040.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225828%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Danielle%20Scott%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8779bfd4fbd083f29846b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224371%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20true%20for%20Danielle%20Scott%2C%20who%20left%20a%2022-year%20career%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20to%20pursue%20interior%20design%20as%20she%20entered%20her%2040s.%20%26quot%3BI%20come%20from%20a%20mom%20who%20was%20in%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20so%20the%20message%20was%20always%20go%20get%20a%20'good%20government%20job%2C'%26quot%3B%20Scott%2C%20now%2041%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20all%20I%20knew%20in%20terms%20of%20guaranteeing%20stability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20became%20a%20GS-15%20at%2028%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20which%20is%20the%20highest%20civilian%20leadership%20ranks%20in%20the%20federal%20government%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20I%20had%20already%20reached%20that%20plateau.%20I%20was%20really%20looking%20for%20what%20the%20next%20challenge%20would%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Scott%20had%20been%20feeling%20the%20lingering%20thoughts%20to%20pivot%20for%20years%2C%20her%20first%20major%20shift%20came%20during%20the%20six-week%20furlough%20under%20the%20first%20Donald%20Trump%20administration%20in%202018.%20The%20pause%20gave%20her%20time%20to%20reflect%20and%20reconsider%20what%20stability%20meant%2C%20especially%20after%20she%20realized%20how%20much%20of%20her%20identity%20had%20been%20tied%20to%20government%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20used%20the%20time%20to%20take%20real%20estate%20and%20interior%20design%20courses%2C%20building%20blocks%20she'd%20one%20day%20depend%20on.%20%26quot%3BI%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20caught%20flat-footed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20she%20turned%2034%2C%20she%20founded%20The%20Styled%20Hause%2C%20an%20interior%20design%20firm.%20Since%20then%2C%20Scott's%20company%20has%20designed%20premium%20suites%20at%20the%20Washington%20Commanders%20stadium%2C%20completed%20commercial%20real%20estate%20projects%20for%20companies%20across%20the%20D.C.%2C%20Maryland%2C%20and%20Virginia%20area%2C%20and%20created%20residential%20spaces%20for%20a%20range%20of%20private%20clients%20%E2%80%94%20from%20professional%20athletes%20to%20music%20executives.%20Along%20the%20way%2C%20they've%20won%20more%20than%2025%20industry%20awards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20what%20once%20felt%20like%20treading%20water%20now%20feels%20like%20a%20blessing%2C%20as%20new%20partnerships%2C%20visibility%2C%20and%20business%20growth%20have%20affirmed%20her%20leap%20into%20entrepreneurship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224371%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Danielle%20Scott%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a877bed3e2f1aef369fbb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225828%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGreg%20Kahn%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221993dc70-3384-4584-a1cf-63e7fe45432a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20midlife%20pivot%20rarely%20has%20to%20do%20with%20career%20boredom%2C%20one%20expert%20said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EExecutive%20coach%20Monique%20Shields%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20professionals%20tend%20to%20pivot%20in%20their%20careers%20in%20their%2040s%2C%20but%20it%20rarely%20stems%20from%20a%20lack%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20assume%20midlife%20pivots%20are%20about%20boredom%2C%26quot%3B%20Shields%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20it%20goes%20much%20deeper%20than%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShields%2C%20who's%20also%20the%20founder%20of%20Seven%20Pines%20Leadership%2C%20a%20development%20firm%20that%20helps%20high-achieving%20women%20grow%20and%20navigate%20career%20transitions%2C%20said%20that%20many%20%26quot%3Barrive%20at%20a%20point%20in%20your%20career%20where%20achievement%20is%20no%20longer%20the%20goal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou've%20done%20all%20the%20striving%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20now%2C%20the%20questions%20become%20more%20about%20well-being%20and%20legacy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20looking%20to%20go%20out%20on%20their%20own%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20misconceptions%20about%20starting%20over%20in%20midlife%20is%20the%20belief%20that%20entrepreneurship%20or%20independent%20work%20will%20be%20significantly%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20fear%20that%20pursuing%20something%20unique%20or%20entrepreneurial%20will%20be%20more%20difficult%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20underestimate%20how%20much%20energy%20they're%20already%20spending%20navigating%20politics%2C%20bureaucracy%2C%20and%20environments%20they%20can't%20control.%20When%20those%20go%20away%2C%20the%20capacity%20you%20gain%20is%20surprising.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20barrier%20to%20making%20the%20entrepreneurial%20jump%2C%20Shields%20said%2C%20is%20often%20fear%20of%20losing%20financial%20stability%2C%20but%20she%20argues%20that%20many%20people%20have%20never%20sat%20down%20to%20examine%20their%20finances%20with%20clarity%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bmost%20are%20surprised%20by%20what's%20actually%20possible%20when%20they%20look%20at%20the%20real%20numbers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20professionals%20approaching%20midlife%2C%20that%20shift%20from%20surviving%20to%20imagining%20is%20often%20the%20first%20step%20toward%20the%20most%20defining%20chapters%20of%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fear%20is%20gone.%20I'm%20not%20operating%20from%20survival%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Neal%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%2020s%20and%2030s%20were%20about%20surviving.%20My%20forties%20are%20about%20execution.%20I'm%20operating%20from%20calling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturning-40-midlife-crisis-career-rebrand-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772706241000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a87701fd4fbd083f298457%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturning-40-midlife-crisis-career-rebrand-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Elder%20millennials%20turn%2040%20and%20begin%20rethinking%20the%20trajectory%20of%20their%20careers.%20Ambitious%20professionals%20are%20using%20the%20moment%20as%20a%20rebrand%20moment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mia%20Davis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fturning-40-midlife-crisis-career-rebrand-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US-Israel%20war%20with%20Iran%3A%2