p%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20have%20asked%20for%20a%20better%20time%20for%20AI%20to%20show%20up%2C%20because%20now%20we%20have%20a%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20growth%20agenda%20ahead%20of%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20its%20corporate%20offices%20in%20Minnesota%2C%20Target%20has%20tech%20employees%20in%20New%20York%2C%20California%2C%20and%20Georgia%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20global%20capability%20center%20in%20Bangalore%2C%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETarget%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-ceo-michael-fiddelke-busy-first-weeks-on-the-job-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esome%20employee%20cuts%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20its%20headquarters%20last%20year%20and%20at%20regional%20teams%20last%20month%20to%20create%20more%20room%20to%20invest%20in%20store%20workers.%20But%20while%20large%20and%20small%20employers%20alike%20are%20citing%20AI%20to%20explain%20their%20shrinking%20tech%20teams%2C%20Vemana%20said%20he%20doesn't%20see%20Target%20doing%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20really%20good%20system%20in%20place%20that%20is%20actually%20putting%20the%20right%20work%20in%20the%20right%20place%2C%20but%20also%20driving%20the%20changes%20that%20we%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20location-specific%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20culture%20that%20we%20are%20building%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20adoption%20of%20AI%20throughout%20the%20enterprise%20among%20coders%2C%20data%20scientists%2C%20cybersecurity%20monitors%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20area%20he%20said%20AI%20coding%20companions%20have%20been%20transformational%20in%20is%20overhauling%20Target's%20mobile%20app%2C%20which%20is%20existentially%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftarget-earnings-results-q4-2025-sales-decline-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimportant%20to%20its%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2