20chin%2C%20the%20wrinkles%20%E2%80%94%20that%20were%20making%20me%20look%20older%20than%20I%20actually%20felt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20very%20busy.%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20energy.%20I%20work%20out%2C%20I'm%20into%20health%2C%20and%20I'm%20very%20active.%20What%20I%20was%20seeing%20in%20the%20mirror%20didn't%20match%20how%20I%20felt%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22986edd85-4a52-4900-96a4-e0ac08ea5ed2%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThree%20years%20ago%2C%20at%2062%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20about%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20wanted%20it%20for%20myself%2C%20but%20I%20also%20knew%20it%20would%20benefit%20my%20work%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20has.%20It's%20given%20me%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%20in%20an%20industry%20filled%20with%20younger%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20now%20had%20several%20procedures%2C%20including%20a%20near-full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacelift-red-flags-from-plastic-surgeon-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efacelift%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20microneedling%2C%20laser%20treatments%20under%20my%20eyes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshould-i-get-botox-pros-cons-undetectable-era-antiaging-treatments-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBotox%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20what's%20called%20an%20eye%20snip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20up%2C%20I've%20spent%20well%20over%20%2433%2C000.%20It's%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things%20I've%20ever%20done%20for%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d3792b04-3a11-4d6f-9aef-14ad291bdad0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIn%20New%20York%20real%20estate%2C%20image%20matters%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20brokers%20in%20their%2080s%20who%20are%20still%20going%20strong%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20perception%20issue%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20you're%20dealing%20with%20younger%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20a%20long%20relationship%20with%20Columbia%20University.%20The%20medical%20school%2C%20the%20law%20school%2C%20and%20the%20general%20campus%20refer%20me%20to%20incoming%20professors%20and%20staff%20who%20are%20relocating%20and%20looking%20to%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20people%20I%20work%20with%20are%20younger%20than%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20them%20to%20feel%20confident%20that%20I%20know%20what%20I'm%20doing%20%E2%80%94%20that%20I%20understand%20technology%2C%20can%20figure%20things%20out%2C%20and%20am%20sharp.%20I%20worried%20that%20my%20face%20was%20aging%20me%20in%20a%20way%20that%20didn't%20reflect%20who%20I%20actually%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20good%20at%20what%20you%20do%2C%20you%20can%20look%20great%2C%20but%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20get%20very%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22476e2b2d-5a21-4718-b875-face77b2f7bf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20first%20procedure%20was%20a%20facelift%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman's%20before%20and%20after%20of%20a%20facelift%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8981cd3e2f1aef369ff35%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDiLeo%20before%20and%20after%20the%20facelift.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dr.%20Kwak%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20first%20got%20a%20facelift%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20full%20one%2C%20but%20pretty%20close.%20It%20cost%20around%20%2428%2C000.%20Annually%2C%20I%20spend%20about%20%241%2C500%20a%20year%20on%20various%20upkeep%20treatments%20like%20Botox.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20chose%20my%20surgeon%2C%20Dr.%20Kwak%2C%20because%20he%20had%20done%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Frhinoplasty%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erhinoplasty%3C%2Fa%3E%20revision%20for%20one%20of%20my%20daughters.%20She'd%20had%20a%20nose%20job%20with%20another%20physician%20that%20didn't%20turn%20out%20well%2C%20and%20he%20completely%20fixed%20it.%20The%20work%20was%20beautiful.%20When%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20for%20myself%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20go%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20I've%20had%20microneedling%2C%20which%20cost%20about%20%243%2C000%2C%20and%20laser%20treatments%20under%20my%20eyes.%20For%20the%20laser%2C%20I%20requested%20general%20anesthesia%20because%20it's%20painful.%20Most%20people%20just%20use%20numbing%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20get%20Botox%2C%20particularly%20in%20my%20neck.%20Most%20recently%2C%20I%20had%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-eye-lift-is-surging-in-popularity-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeye%20snip%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20they%20remove%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20skin%20under%20the%20lower%20lash%20line%20to%20smooth%20wrinkles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20and%20out%20of%20the%20office%20in%20about%20an%20hour%20and%20a%20half%2C%20awake%20the%20whole%20time.%20I've%20been%20happy%20with%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e1ee1b34-2982-4a77-bad4-ada69920b9ea%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20assume%20cosmetic%20surgery%20is%20about%20wanting%20to%20look%20younger%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20it%20wasn't%20that.%20It%20was%20about%20looking%20more%20like%20how%20I%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20very%20empowering%20to%20look%20in%20the%20mirror%2C%20see%20something%20you're%20unhappy%20about%2C%20and%20realize%20you%20can%20actually%20do%20something%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20when%20I%20walk%20into%20a%20work%20cocktail%20party%20with%20people%20in%20their%2020s%20and%2030s%2C%20I%20don't%20feel%20out%20of%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20confident%2C%20and%20confidence%20matters%20more%20than%20people%20like%20to%20admit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afa34777-3af9-47e5-9cac-4745c1f412bf%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20haven't%20been%20shy%20about%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20ashamed%20of%20anything.%20If%20people%20ask%20me%2C%20I%20tell%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20nothing%20but%20positive%20feedback.%20Sometimes%20I'll%20see%20someone%20I%20haven't%20seen%20in%20a%20while%2C%20and%20they'll%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20look%20great.%26quot%3B%20I%20joke%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20uphill%20battle%20%E2%80%94%20fighting%20age%20isn't%20for%20sissies!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20probably%20too%20big%20a%20statement%2C%20but%20it%20was%20life-changing%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20in%20both%20my%20career%20and%20personal%20confidence.%20It%20really%20gave%20me%20a%20lot%20more%20confidence%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20best%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-33000-cosmetic-procedures-boosted-confidence-career-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772705101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a897dcd3e2f1aef369ff30%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-33000-cosmetic-procedures-boosted-confidence-career-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Susan%20DiLeo%20is%20a%2065-year-old%20real-estate%20agent%20based%20in%20New%20York%20City.%20She's%20had%20a%20near-full%20facelift%2C%20microneedling%2C%20laser%20treatments%2C%20and%20Botox.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Elle%20Hardy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-33000-cosmetic-procedures-boosted-confidence-career-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gambhir%20attends%20Arjun's%20wedding%20hours%20before%20Ind%20vs%20Eng%20T20%20WC%20SF%20-%20Watch%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772705072000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129083775%2Cimgsize-1360093.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Foff-the-field%2Fgautam-gambhir-attends-arjun-tendulkars-wedding-hours-before-india-