n%3EVinod%20Khosla%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20investors%20in%20OpenAI%2C%20said%20he%20believes%20AI%20is%20so%20powerful%2C%20today's%20toddlers%20won't%20need%20to%20work.%3Cp%3ECOLE%20BURSTON%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOpenAI%20investor%20Vinod%20Khosla%20predicts%2080%25%20of%20jobs%20will%20be%20done%20by%20AI%20by%20the%20early%202030s.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20AI%20investor%20joins%20a%20list%20of%20high-earning%20executives%20who%20have%20warned%20about%20the%20future%20of%20jobs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20frames%20the%20battle%20between%20the%20US%20and%20China%20for%20AI%20dominance%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btechno-economic%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EBillionaire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvinod-khosla-looks-at-this-metric-to-gauge-ai-bubble-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eventure%20capitalist%20Vinod%20Khosla%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20most%20of%20today's%20children%20won't%20need%20jobs%20when%20they%20grow%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcSWvm7nu1rI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFortune%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Sun%20Microsystems%20cofounder%20and%20tech%20investor%20predicted%20that%20artificial%20intelligence%20will%20be%20able%20to%20do%20up%20to%2080%25%20of%20jobs%20by%20the%20early%202030s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20pretty%20unlikely%20a%20five-year-old%20today%20will%20be%20looking%20for%20a%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhosla%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Khosla%20Ventures%2C%20has%20built%20a%20reputation%20for%20making%20bold%2C%20well-timed%20technology%20bets.%20He%20was%20the%20first%20institutional%20investor%20in%20OpenAI%20in%202019%2C%20investing%20%2450%20million%20at%20a%20%241%20billion%20valuation%20%E2%80%94%20the%20largest%20initial%20investment%20of%20his%20career%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20interview%2C%20released%20Wednesday%2C%20he%20argued%20that%20rapid%20advances%20in%20AI%20and%20robotics%20will%20make%20most%20labor%20effectively%20free%20within%2015%20years%2C%20creating%20an%20era%20of%20extreme%20abundance%20and%20lower%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20money-making%20occupations%2C%20he%20said%2C%20people%20will%20pursue%20their%20passions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20need%20to%20work%20will%20go%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20will%20still%20work%20on%20the%20things%20they%20want%20to%20work%20on%2C%20not%20because%20they%20need%20to%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20manual%20labor%20jobs%20like%20assembly-line%20roles%20and%20farm%20work%2C%20Khosla%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThose%20are%20not%20jobs.%20Those%20are%20servitude.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKhosla%20is%20the%20latest%20in%20a%20line%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%20executives%20who%20believe%20that%20some%20of%20today's%20most%20sought-after%20jobs%20might%20soon%20fade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Boris%20Cherny%3Cstrong%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20creator%20of%20Claude%20Code%2C%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20AI%20will%20make%20the%20job%20title%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-claude-code-founder-ai-impacts-software-engineer-role-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esoftware%20engineer%20%26quot%3Bgo%20away%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20starting%20next%20year.%20Dario%20Amodei%2C%20Anthropic's%20CEO%2C%20also%20said%20he%20believes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-ceo-warning-ai-could-eliminate-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20could%20soon%20eliminate%2050%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20entry-level%20office%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvinod-khosla-ai-taxes-capital-labor-job-losses-billionaires-musk-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKhosla%20said%20his%20vision%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20not%20apocalyptic%20%E2%80%94%20but%20only%20if%20America%20beats%20its%20competitors%20with%20better%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20framed%20the%20US-China%20AI%20competition%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btechno-economic%20war%2C%26quot%3B%20arguing%20that%20whoever%20wins%20the%20race%20will%20shape%20global%20economic%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhoever%20wins%20that%20war%2C%20he%20said%2C%20will%20also%20enjoy%20a%20world%20filled%20with%20abundant%20tech%2C%20lower%20prices%2C%20and%20less%20human%20exploitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20suspect%20by%202040%2C%20%2430%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20and%20maybe%20%2410%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20will%20buy%20much%20more%20than%20you%20can%20buy%20if%20you%20have%20a%20%24100%2C000%20income%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvinod-khosla-5-year-olds-wont-need-job-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772704621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a87c451fb3fcb42648ea00%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvinod-khosla-5-year-olds-wont-need-job-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vinod%20Khosla%2C%20a%20billionaire%20investor%20with%20a%20long%20history%20of%20anticipating%20upcoming%20tech%2C%20said%20he%20thinks%20AI%20will%20soon%20replace%20millions%20of%20jobs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bshimkus%40insider.com%20(Ben%20Shimkus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvinod-khosla-5-year-olds-wont-need-job-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20Better%20Alternative%20Than%20Us'%3A%20US%20Official%20On%20India's%20Russian%20Oil%20Purchase%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Christopher%20Landau's%20remarks%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India's%20energy%20sourcing%20is%20under%20renewed%20pressure%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20