tand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harvard%2C%20Yale%20Among%2022%20Universities%20Banned%20By%20US%20For%20Military%20Education%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22The%20Pentagon%20is%20also%20cutting%20ties%20with%20several%20think%20tanks%20known%20for%20defence%20and%20national%20security%20research.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772702249000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-02%2Faun5krls_harvard_625x300_15_February_26.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fharvard-yale-brown-among-22-universities-banned-by-us-for-military-education-11171038%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Pentagon%20is%20also%20cutting%20ties%20with%20several%20think%20tanks%20known%20for%20defence%20and%20national%20security%20research.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fharvard-yale-brown-among-22-universities-banned-by-us-for-military-education-11171038%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kalshi's%20response%20to%20its%20%242.2%20million%20Iran%20mess%3A%20More%20fine%20print%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224660%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kalshi%20logo%20on%20phone%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8a982d3e2f1aef36a01f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223107%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKristian%20Tuxen%20Ladegaard%20Berg%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EKalshi%20sparked%20outrage%20over%20how%20it%20handled%20bets%20tied%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20Iranian%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ali%20Khamenei.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20it%20announced%20a%20proposed%20rule%20to%20quiet%20those%20who%20have%20said%20it's%20running%20a%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20market.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPrediction%20markets%20say%20they%20cut%20through%20the%20noise%2C%20but%20the%20rules%20are%20anything%20but%20simple%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prediction%20market%20Kalshi%20wants%20you%20to%20know%20that%20it%20definitely%20doesn't%20run%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20markets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cftc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Ffilings%2Forgrules%2F26%2F03%2Frules03022640155.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enotice%3C%2Fa%3E%20filed%20Monday%2C%20the%20company%20proposed%20standardizing%20the%20terms%20of%20all%20its%20markets%20that%20implicitly%20depend%20on%20a%20person%20surviving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20person%20dies%2C%20according%20to%20the%20new%20rule%2C%20all%20bets%20related%20to%20them%20will%20be%20paid%20out%20at%20the%20odds%20that%20existed%20just%20before%20they%20died%20or%20their%20death%20was%20%26quot%3Breasonably%20anticipated%20by%20market%20participants.%26quot%3B%20The%20rule%20goes%20into%20effect%20March%2017%2C%20according%20to%20the%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20update%20comes%20after%20Kalshi%20paid%20%242.2%20million%20to%20resolve%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkhamenei-prediction-markets-kalshi-polymarket-insider-trading-outrage-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomplaints%20from%20users%20who%20were%20confused%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20way%20it%20divided%20the%20%2455%20million%20wagered%20on%20Iran's%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ali%20Khamenei's%20ouster%20after%20his%20targeted%20killing%20by%20Israel%20and%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20different%20Kalshi%20markets%20could%20have%20been%20resolved%20in%20different%20ways%20when%20a%20person%20who%20is%20central%20to%20the%20wager%20dies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20point%20of%20the%20change%2C%20Kalshi%20said%2C%20was%20to%20%26quot%3Bminimize%20market%20disruption%2C%20minimize%20perverse%20incentives%2C%20and%20protect%20the%20markets.%26quot%3B%20It%20was%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdan_bernstein_%2Fstatus%2F2028626239473205481%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflagged%20on%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20journalist%20Dan%20Bernstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsers%20weren't%20the%20only%20ones%20up%20in%20arms%20about%20the%20Khamenei%20killing.%20Federal%20regulations%20prohibit%20making%20markets%20based%20on%20assassination%2C%20war%2C%20terrorism%2C%20and%20certain%20other%20topics.%20On%20Saturday%2C%20Sen.%20Chris%20Murphy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fchrismurphyct%2Fstatus%2F2027899652226326800%3Fs%3D46%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20X%20that%20he%20would%20introduce%20legislation%20to%20ban%20%26quot%3Bprofiting%20off%20war%20and%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Khamenei%20episode%2C%20and%20Kalshi's%20response%2C%20are%20the%20latest%20examples%20of%20growing%20pains%20for%20the%20burgeoning%20prediction%20markets%20industry.%20Though%20they've%20bragged%20about%20their%20ability%20to%20%26quot%3Bcut%20through%20the%20chaos%2C%26quot%3B%20prediction%20markets%20are%20increasingly%20confronting%20the%20complexity%20and%20messiness%20of%20the%20real%20world%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20fine%20print%20of%20their%20rulebooks%20is%20only%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20rival%20Polymarket%20has%20taken%20a%20decidedly%20laissez-faire%20approach%2C%20Kalshi%20appears%20to%20be%20positioning%20itself%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20now%20sort%20of%20this%20nascent%2C%20but%20bipartisan%20movement%20against%20prediction%20markets.%20I%20think%20Kalshi's%20feeling%20the%20heat%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Karl%20Lockhart%2C%20a%20law%20professor%20at%20DePaul%20University%20who%20has%20followed%20the%20industry.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20trying%20to%20say%2C%20'We're%20not%20the%20outlandish%20one.%20We're%20the%20middle-of-the-road%20prediction%20market.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2289e50521-bd85-4027-b027-5c716fcd83e9%5C%22%3EKalshi%20has%20over%2067%2C591%20words%20of%20rules%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20popular%20events%20that%20people%20trade%20on%20Kalshi%20and%20Polymarket%20relate%20to%20sports%20and%20cryptocurrency.%20Together%2C%20those%20categories%20amount%20to%20roughly%2090%25%20of%20the%20activity%20on%20Kalshi%2C%20and%2060%20to%2070%25%20of%20activity%20on%20Polymarket%2C%20according%20to%20user-generated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdune.com%2Fdatadashboards%2Fprediction-markets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edashboards%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20analytics%20website%20Dune.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20other%20markets%20draw%20a%20disproportionate%20amount%20of%20attention%20from%20the%20news%20media%20and%20government%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20are%20helpful%20to%20economists%20and%20policymakers.%20Polymarket's%20accuracy%20increases%20to%20over%2090%25%20as%20events%20draw%20nearer%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdune.com%2Falexmccullough%2Fhow-accurate-is-polymarket%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresearch%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20prediction%20market%20analyst%20Alex%20McCullough.%20And%20recent%20Kalshi%20estimates%20on%20the%20US%20consumer%20price%20index%20have%20tended%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fopen.substack.com%2Fpub%2Ffiftycentdollars%2Fp%2Fminimum-viable-liquidity%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewithin%200.1%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20official%20number.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20markets%20have%20been%20controversial.%20Kalshi%20posted%20about%20its%20market%20on%20Khamenei's%20ousting%20after%2010%20a.m.%20ET%20on%20February%2028%20%E2%80%94%20before%20stopping%20trading%20several%20hours%20later.%20It%20decided%20to%20pay%20contract%20holders%20based%20on%20the%20probabilities%20of%20Khamenei%20being%20%26quot%3Bout%26quot%3B%20as%20they%20stood%20one%20minute%20before%20bombs%20and%20missiles%20began%20to%20fall%20on%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicholas%20Mahoney%2C%20a%2030-year-old%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F48fund.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eenergy%20finance%20entrepreneur%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20wagered%20%244%2C800%20on%20the%20Khamenei%20market%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Kalshi's%20resolution%20felt%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bbait-and-switch.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20it%20was%20his%20second%20time%20using%20Kalshi%2C%20and%20the%20experience%20left%20a%20bad%20enough%20impression%20that%20he%20emptied%20his%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20death-markets%20rule%20was%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cftc.gov%2FIndustryOversight%2FIndustryFilings%2FPTCDCMRules%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eseveral%20new%20filings%3C%2Fa%3E%20Kalshi%20lodged%20with%20the%20US%20Commodity%20Futures%20Trading%20Commission%20this%20week.%20Kalshi%20users%20have%20to%20agree%20to%20more%20than%20180%20pages%20of%20terms%2C%20rules%2C%20and%20policies%2C%20totalling%20over%2067%2C591%20words%2C%20when%20they%20create%20an%20account%20and%20when%20they%20log%20in%2C%20and%20each%20individual%20contract%20has%20its%20own%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20users%20don't%20read%20them%2C%20but%20diehard%20traders%20say%20they%20can%20be%20helpful%20to%20resolve%20edge%20cases.%20In%20late%20February%2C%20Kalshi%20filed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cftc.gov%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Ffilings%2Fptc%2F26%2F02%2Fptc02262639929.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eupdate%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20its%20%26quot%3Bmention%26quot%3B%20market%20rules%20%E2%80%94%20where%20users%20bet%20on%20what%20politicians%2C%20celebrities%20and%20corporate%20executives%20will%20say%20in%20upcoming%20public%20remarks%20%E2%80%94%20that%20runs%20eight%20pages.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkalshi-public-docs.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcontract_terms%2FMENTION.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexisting%20mention-markets%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20by%20comparison%2C%20are%20two%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalshi%20said%20that%20it%20resolved%20the%20%26quot%3BKhamenei%20out%26quot%3B%20market%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkalshi-public-docs.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcontract_terms%2FWLEADEROUT.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWLEADEROUT%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20were%20attached%20to%20the%20market.%20It%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20users%20might%20not%20have%20been%20aware%20of%20the%20rules%20because%20of%20how%20its%20website%20and%20app%20are%20designed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Kalshi%20updated%20its%20%26quot%3BWho%20will%20be%20the%20next%20Supreme%20Leader%20of%20Iran%3F%26quot%3B%20market%2C%20where%20more%20than%20%246.4%20million%20in%20contracts%20have%20been%20struck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkalshi.com%2Fmarkets%2Fkxnextiranleader%2Fwho-will-be-khameneis-successor%2Fkxnextiranleader-45jan01%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etitle%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20prominently%20includes%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20settles%20to%20last%20traded%20price.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2228eaa05e-a0bb-4247-a6a7-34c83ed2186b%5C%22%3EFederal%20rules%20are%20coming%20to%20prediction%20markets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPolymarket%20is%20very%20different%20from%20Kalshi.%20While%20it%20has%20a%20small%2C%20US-regulated%20operation%20that%20the%20general%20public%20cannot%20currently%20sign%20up%20for%2C%20most%20action%20takes%20place%20using%20cryptocurrency%20on%20a%20market%20that%20is%20legally%20based%20in%20Panama.%20While%20it%20has%20advertised%20heavily%20in%20the%20US%2C%20American%20users%20must%20mask%20their%20location%20if%20they%20want%20to%20trade%20on%20the%20international%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPolymarket%20has%20much%20more%20threadbare%20rules%20than%20Kalshi%2C%20and%20many%20of%20its%20markets%20are%20resolved%20according%20to%20a%20decentralized%20process%20that%20Polymarket%20has%20been%20known%20to%20weigh%20in%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20markets%20exist%20on%20Polymarket%20than%20on%20Kalshi%2C%20including%20some%20that%20could%20violate%20US%20regulations%20about%20markets%20for%20illegal%20activity.%20Last%20year%2C%20several%20men%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Fathletic%2F6541093%2F2025%2F08%2F07%2Fwnba-sex-toy-incidents-cryptocurrency-group-scheme%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Earrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20throwing%20sex%20toys%20onto%20the%20court%20at%20women's%20professional%20basketball%20games%3B%20Polymarket%20hosted%20markets%20asking%20whether%20it%20would%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20%24802%20million%20was%20traded%20on%20Iran-related%20bets%20on%20Polymarket%2C%20most%20of%20which%20was%20tied%20to%20the%20chances%20of%20a%20US%20strike%2C%20according%20to%20research%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FPredictefy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPredictefy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20analytics%20firm.%20That%20compares%20to%20less%20than%20%2480%20million%20across%20a%20handful%20of%20Iran%20markets%20on%20Kalshi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20didn't%20respond%20to%20questions%20about%20whether%20it%20would%20consider%20limiting%20death%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeveral%20markets%20on%20Polymarket%20have%20been%20marred%20by%20allegations%20of%20insider%20trading%2C%20with%20analysts%20flagging%20new%20accounts%20that%20made%20well-timed%20bets%20on%20US%20and%20Israeli%20military%20activity%2C%20including%20the%20attacks%20on%20Iran%20and%20the%20arrest%20of%20Venezuelan%20leader%20Nicolas%20Maduro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichael%20Selig%2C%20who%20chairs%20the%20CFTC%2C%20said%20at%20an%20event%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20the%20agency%20was%20drafting%20rules%20for%20what%20it%20terms%20%26quot%3Bevent%20contracts.%26quot%3B%20That%20process%20could%20take%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrediction%20markets%20have%20grown%20so%20much%20and%20so%20quickly%2C%20and%20they're%20being%20offered%20on%20such%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20events%2C%20that%20rulesmaking%20is%20right%20now%20a%20major%20component%20of%20building%20credibility%20in%20these%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Harry%20Crane%2C%20a%20statistics%20professor%20at%20Rutgers%20University%20who%20has%20studied%20and%20used%20prediction%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-iran-prediction-market-death-rule-fine-print-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772702221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8aadcfd4fbd083f298ae1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-iran-prediction-market-death-rule-fine-print-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kalshi%20is%20proposing%20a%20new%20rule%20after%20complaints%20over%20its%20Khamenei%20%26quot%3Bdeath%20market.%26quot%3B%20The%20prediction%20markets'%20rulebooks%20are%20only%20getting%20longer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jnewsham%40insider.com%20(Jack%20Newsham)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkalshi-iran-prediction-market-death-rule-fine-print-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tax%20Haven%2C%20USA%3A%20Mapping%20the%20tiny%20tax%20shelters%20scattered%20across%20America%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225609%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20shot%20of%20mansions%20in%20a%20wealthy%20neighborhood%20in%20California%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8b095d3e2f1aef36a02b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223743%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Edszc%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%20a%20long%20session%20at%20the%20high-ceilinged%20New%20Jersey%20Assembly%20Building%20in%20early%20May%201967%2C%20Assemblyman%20Vito%20Albanese%20rose%20to%20his%20feet%20and%20announced%20that%20someone%20had%20tried%20to%20bribe%20him%20to%20kill%20a%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20assembly%20floor%20exploded%20in%20response%2C%20with%20members%20shouting%20and%20leaping%20to%20their%20feet%2C%20as%20the%20speaker%20banged%20his%20gavel%20to%20quiet%20the%20crowd.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20question%2C%26quot%3B%20Albanese%2C%20a%20stout%2C%20white-haired%20Democrat%2C%20shouted%20over%20the%20noise.%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I%20tell%20you%2C%20I%20was%20approached!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20in%20question%20would%20have%20dissolved%20the%20town%20of%20Teterboro%2C%20New%20Jersey%20%E2%80%94%20a%20tiny%20municipality%20that%20at%20the%20time%20consisted%20of%20only%20two%20residential%20streets%2C%2017%20residents%2C%20and%2050%20businesses.%20Spread%20across%20a%20square%20mile%20of%20converted%20swampland%2C%20Teterboro%20was%20designed%20as%20an%20admitted%20tax%20haven%2C%20a%20legal%20gimmick%20in%20which%20a%20friendly%20regulatory%20environment%20and%20low%20tax%20rates%20would%20lure%20business%20investment%20to%20the%20bare%20bones%20town.%20The%2017%20Teterboroans%20paid%20no%20property%20taxes%20and%20the%2050%20businesses%20enjoyed%20an%20industrial%20tax%20rate%20of%2059%20cents%20per%20%24100%20of%20assessed%20value%2C%20by%20far%20the%20lowest%20in%20northern%20New%20Jersey.%20Albanese's%20bill%20aimed%20to%20legislate%20the%20tax%20haven%20out%20of%20existence%2C%20spreading%20its%20substantial%20property%20tax%20wealth%20among%20several%20more%20resource-poor%20neighboring%20towns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20high-stakes%20investigation%20played%20out%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20detailed%20in%20New%20York%20Times%20archives.%20Albanese%20laid%20out%20his%20allegations%2C%20accusing%20a%20former%20prosecutor%20of%20approaching%20him%20at%20a%20meeting%20of%20business%20leaders%20and%20whispering%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20name%20your%20own%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20ear.%20Another%20New%20Jersey%20politician%20added%20that%20he'd%20received%20a%20call%20from%20the%20Teterboro%20police%20chief%20who%20had%20warned%20him%20of%20%26quot%3Bimplied%20bodily%20injury%20and%20personal%20and%20business%20losses%2C%26quot%3B%20if%20he%20continued%20to%20support%20the%20bill.%20In%20the%20end%2C%20the%20legislature's%20investigation%20dismissed%20Albanese's%20bribery%20charge%20for%20lack%20of%20evidence%2C%20describing%20his%20accusations%20as%20an%20instance%20of%20%26quot%3BMcCarthyism.%26quot%3B%20The%20bill%20to%20dissolve%20Teterboro%20collapsed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Teterboro%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a904f7fd4fbd083f298dd5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETeterboro%3Cp%3EGuthrie%20Scrimgeour%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20day%2C%20the%20bizarre%20town%20continues%20to%20exist.%20Teterboro%20is%20more%20a%20mall%20than%20a%20town%2C%20with%20a%20Walmart%2C%20a%20Costco%2C%20an%20Outback%20Steakhouse%2C%20and%20dozens%20of%20industrial%20businesses%20flanked%20by%20two%20highways%20%E2%80%94%20and%20about%2060%20residents.%20It%20holds%20%24455%20million%20in%20property%20tax%20wealth%2C%20or%20%247.3%20million%20per%20resident%2C%2045%20times%20more%20wealth%20per%20capita%20than%20Teterboro's%20surrounding%20metro%20area.%20The%20Teterboro%20website%20boasts%20that%20they%20offer%20the%20lowest%20tax%20rates%20in%20the%20county.%20Taxes%20are%20so%20low%2C%20says%20Teterboro%20Municipal%20Manager%20Nick%20Saros%2C%20because%20the%20town%20doesn't%20fund%20a%20local%20school%20system%20and%20most%20services%20are%20provided%20by%20surrounding%20towns%20via%20interlocal%20agreements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20tremendous%2C%20terrific%20tax%20rate%2C%20and%20we're%20geographically%20located%20in%20a%20beautiful%20area%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Saros.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20unique%20town.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeterboro%20is%20pretty%20unique%2C%20but%20it%20isn't%20entirely%20alone.%20The%20United%20States%20is%20dotted%20with%20hundreds%20of%20similar%20enclaves%20that%20function%20as%20miniature%20tax%20havens%20for%20property%20tax%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20new%20study%20published%20in%20the%20Socio-Economic%20Review%2C%20the%20researchers%20Brian%20Highsmith%20and%20Robert%20Manduca%20analyzed%20138%20million%20property%20tax%20records%20across%20America%20to%20assemble%20a%20list%20of%20more%20than%20500%20municipalities%20in%20which%20the%20taxable%20wealth%20per%20capita%20is%20more%20than%20three%20times%20that%20of%20the%20surrounding%20metro%20area.%20They%20describe%20these%20places%20as%20%26quot%3Bmunicipal%20tax%20havens%2C%26quot%3B%20because%20they%20hoard%20vast%20sums%20of%20taxable%20property%20tax%20wealth%20that%20could%20otherwise%20be%20distributed%20amongst%20the%20surrounding%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20include%20famously%20wealthy%20suburbs%20like%20Beverly%20Hills%20and%20various%20towns%20dotting%20the%20Hamptons%2C%20but%20also%20relatively%20unknown%20industry-friendly%20towns%20with%20few%20residents%20like%20Teterboro.%20%26quot%3BThese%20jurisdictions%20effectively%20function%20as%20tax%20shelters%20for%20their%20residents%20and%20corporations%2C%20allowing%20access%20to%20the%20broader%20metropolitan%20economy%20without%20contributing%20to%20local%20spending%20programs%20benefiting%20neighboring%20jurisdictions%2C%26quot%3B%20Highsmith%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wealth%20these%20municipal%20tax%20havens%20hold%20is%20enormous%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20filled%20with%20multimillion-dollar%20homes%20and%20prosperous%20business%20centers.%20The%20top%20100%20most%20fragmented%20enclaves%20the%20report%20identified%20hold%20more%20than%20%24200%20billion%20in%20property%20tax%20wealth.%20The%20top%20500%20hold%20more%20than%20%241.2%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20taxation%20methods%20are%20different%20state%20to%20state%2C%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20these%20towns%20actually%20shield%20their%20tax%20wealth%20varies.%20But%20generally%2C%20being%20incorporated%20allows%20these%20places%20to%20hoard%20significant%20chunks%20of%20their%20taxable%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20property%20taxes%20are%20the%20most%20substantial%20funding%20source%20for%20local%20governments%2C%20accounting%20for%2072%20percent%20of%20total%20local%20tax%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fitep.org%2Fhow-local-governments-raise-revenue-2024%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLocal%2520Taxes%3A%2520A%2520Nationwide%2520View%26amp%3Btext%3DProperty%2520taxes%2520account%2520for%252072%2Cmake%2520up%2520the%2520remaining%2520portion.%26amp%3Btext%3DLocal%2520taxes%2520altogether%2520provide%2520over%2Ctax%2520policies%2520and%2520stronger%2520communities.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevenue%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20this%20fragmentation%20of%20property%20tax%20wealth%20impacts%20local%20budgets.%20The%20report%20finds%20that%20while%20wealthy%20enclaves%20benefit%20from%20this%20setup%20through%20lower%20property%20tax%20rates%20or%20higher%20revenue%2C%20their%20neighbors%20are%20often%20financially%20strapped%2C%20losing%20out%20on%20revenue%20and%20struggling%20to%20make%20local%20budgets%20pencil%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20fiscal%20distress%20is%20not%20inevitable%2C%20nor%20even%20necessarily%20linked%20to%20deindustrialization%20or%20broad%20economic%20trends%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Highsmith.%20%26quot%3BIt%20reflects%2C%20at%20least%20in%20part%2C%20the%20way%20that%20the%20US%20fiscal%20system%20allows%20wealth%20to%20evade%20redistributive%20local%20taxation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20early%2020th%20century%20America%2C%20new%20towns%20were%20popping%20up%20left%20and%20right.%20Lax%20incorporation%20laws%20led%20to%20thousands%20of%20small%20suburbs%20breaking%20off%20from%20their%20larger%20metro%20area%20to%20become%20Hills%2C%20Heights%2C%20Woods%2C%20and%20Villages.%20Today%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%2090%2C000%20independent%20jurisdictions%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20common%20that%20manufacturing%20concerns%20or%20businesses%20would%20incorporate%20their%20little%20area%20to%20avoid%20regulation%20and%20higher%20taxes%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Jon%20Teaford%2C%20a%20professor%20at%20Purdue%20who%20studies%20urban%20history.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20a%20snob%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20Certain%20wealthy%20enclaves%20were%20incorporated%20and%20zoned%20specifically%20to%20ensure%20that%20they%20would%20%26quot%3Bremain%20a%20high%20class%20residential%20area.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20happened%20in%20Indian%20Creek%20Village%2C%20a%20tiny%20island%20city%20of%2080%20people%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Miami%20that%20now%20sits%20at%20the%20top%20of%20Highsmith%20and%20Manduca's%20list%20of%20municipal%20tax%20havens.%20Dredged%20from%20the%20Biscayne%20Bay%20and%20incorporated%20in%201936%2C%20the%20town%20was%20envisioned%20from%20its%20earliest%20days%20as%20a%20haven%20for%20the%20super-rich.%20It's%20centered%20around%20a%20%24500%2C000-a-year%20golf%20club%2C%20which%20takes%20up%2080%20percent%20of%20the%20island%2C%20and%20is%20surrounded%20by%20a%20ring%20of%20mansions%20owned%20by%20millionaires%20and%20billionaires%20like%20Jeff%20Bezos%2C%20Jared%20Kushner%2C%20Carl%20Icahn%2C%20and%2C%20most%20recently%2C%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20%E2%80%94%20earning%20its%20nickname%2C%20the%20Billionaire%20Bunker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20its%20status%20as%20an%20independent%20municipality%2C%20much%20of%20Indian%20Creek's%20%24934.8%20million%20in%20property%20tax%20value%20(%2411.1%20million%20per%20resident)%20is%20shielded%20from%20the%20broader%20metro%20area.%20The%20town%20keeps%20property%20tax%20rates%20low%20and%20spends%20its%20%246%20million%20budget%20almost%20entirely%20on%20personal%20security%2C%20chartering%20a%20police%20force%20of%2020%20officers%20who%20run%20a%20non-stop%20patrol%20in%20speedboats%2C%20ticketing%20any%20boaters%20who%20roam%20too%20close%20to%20their%20shores.%20Visitors%20get%20the%20distinct%20sense%20that%20the%20island%20is%20a%20fortress%2C%20with%20a%20level%20of%20security%20more%20similar%20to%20a%20military%20installation%20than%20a%20town.%20The%20one%20bridge%20to%20the%20island%20is%20guarded%20by%20Indian%20Creek%20police%2C%20who%20only%20allow%20residents%20and%20those%20with%20approved%20business%20to%20enter.%20The%20perimeter%20is%20dotted%20with%20cameras%20and%20the%20red%20lights%20of%20a%20newly%20installed%20radar-system%20follow%20the%20movements%20of%20passing%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20500%20tax%20havens%20that%20Highsmith%20and%20Manduca%20identify%2C%20100%20are%20considered%20%26quot%3Bcorporate%20enclaves%2C%26quot%3B%20where%2075%20percent%20of%20tax%20wealth%20is%20non-residential.%20One%20extreme%20example%20of%20the%20corporate%20enclave%20is%20Champ%2C%20Missouri.%20It%20was%20founded%20in%201959%20by%20Bill%20Bangert%2C%20a%206'5%26quot%3B%2C%20blind-in-one-eye%2C%20self-described%20%26quot%3BWorld's%20Strongest%20Mayor%26quot%3B%20who%20dreamed%20of%20building%20what%20he%20called%20a%20%26quot%3Bcontrolled%20municipality%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20facilitate%20the%20construction%20of%20a%20massive%20mall%20and%20a%20%2489%20million%20stadium%20in%20hopes%20of%20luring%20the%20Olympic%20games%20to%20the%20St.%20Louis%20suburbs.%20By%201967%2C%20the%20town%20had%20only%2012%20residents%20who%20paid%20no%20property%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChamp's%20Olympic%20dreams%20never%20came%20to%20fruition%2C%20but%20the%20town%20retained%20its%20status%20as%20anindependent%20municipality%2C%20eventually%20attracting%20an%20industrial%20landfill.%20Today%2C%20its%20population%20has%20declined%20to%2010%2C%20according%20to%20the%20census.%20The%20landfill%20now%20makes%20up%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20town's%20property%20tax%20wealth%2C%20%2420%20million%2C%20or%20%242%20million%20per%20resident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sagaponack%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8c2721fb3fcb42648f1d6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESagaponack%3Cp%3EGuthrie%20Scrimgeour%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20more%20recent%20incorporation%20occurred%20in%202005%20in%20the%20Village%20of%20Sagaponack%20near%20the%20tip%20of%20Long%20Island.%20The%20village%2C%20which%20has%20been%20home%20to%20artists%20like%20Kurt%20Vonnegut%20and%20Drew%20Barrymore%2C%20along%20with%20scores%20of%20millionaires%20and%20billionaires%2C%20is%20an%20unusual%20mix%20of%20rustic%20pastoral%20charm%20and%20unimaginable%20wealth.%20The%20recently%20remodelled%20Sagaponack%20General%20Store%20has%20a%20gilded%20log%20cabin%20feel%2C%20offering%20free%20range%20rotisserie%20chickens%20and%20a%20%2424.99%20six-pack%20of%20Corona.%20It's%20run%20by%20Mindy%20Gray%2C%20the%20billionaire%20wife%20of%20Blackstone%20Chief%20Operating%20Officer%20Jonathan%20Gray.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20epicenter%20of%20Sagaponack%20wealth%20sits%20billionaire%20Ira%20Rennert's%20mega-mansion%2C%20which%20he's%20christened%20%26quot%3BFair%20Field.%26quot%3B%20The%20property%2C%20whose%20indoor%20floor%20space%20would%20span%20two%20football%20fields%2C%20features%20several%20swimming%20pools%20and%20tennis%20courts%2C%20a%20bowling%20alley%2C%20synagogue%2C%20100-car%20garage%2C%20and%20private%20power%20plant.%20It's%20valued%20at%20%24450%20million%2C%20about%201%2C000%20times%20more%20than%20the%20average%20American%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20told%2C%20Sagaponack%20holds%20%246.3%20billion%20of%20taxable%20property%20wealth%2C%20or%20%248.2%20million%20for%20each%20of%20its%20771%20residents.%20Though%20most%20of%20its%20taxes%20are%20still%20paid%20to%20the%20larger%20town%20of%20Southampton%2C%20Sagaponack%20has%20managed%20to%20keep%20its%20property%20taxes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.empirecenter.org%2Fpublications%2Flocal-new-york-property-taxes-ranked-by-empire-center-2%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20often%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2006%2F11%2F26%2Fnyregion%2Fimmense-wealth-and-the-lowest-taxes.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20lowest%20effective%20tax%20rates%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20while%20laws%20around%20incorporating%20new%20municipalities%20have%20made%20the%20practice%20increasingly%20rare%2C%20the%20impacts%20of%20the%20incorporation%20rush%20remain.%20In%20their%20research%20of%20town%20budget%20data%20from%20the%20U.S.%20Census%2C%20Highsmith%20and%20Manduca%20conclude%20that%20this%20sort%20of%20fragmentation%20meaningfully%20shapes%20public%20spending.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20tax%20base-poor%20jurisdictions%20partially%20compensate%20by%20turning%20to%20other%20revenue%20sources%20or%20taxing%20local%20property%20wealth%20at%20higher%20rates%2C%20this%20is%20not%20sufficient%20to%20compensate%20for%20their%20lower%20levels%20of%20own-source%20fiscal%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20write.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%2010%20miles%20away%20from%20Teterboro%20is%20one%20such%20have-not%20jurisdiction%2C%20Newark.%20The%20city%20has%20%2449%2C050%20in%20property%20tax%20wealth%20per%20capita%2C%20about%20150%20times%20less%20than%20their%20tax%20haven%20neighbor.%20Newark%20struggles%20to%20obtain%20bonds%20for%20infrastructure%20and%20is%20frequently%20cash%20strapped%2C%20relying%20on%20loans%20from%20the%20state%20to%20cover%20budget%20shortfalls.%20Voters%20rejected%20a%20proposal%20to%20increase%20the%20city%20income%20tax%20last%20November%2C%20and%20they%20now%20face%20a%20projected%20budget%20deficit%20which%20may%20lead%20the%20city%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20street%20paving.%20It's%20a%20struggle%20that%20can%20be%20at%20least%20partially%20attributed%20to%20their%20small%20tax%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Factivest.org%2Fnewark-new-jersey-fiscal-justice-analysis%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DSome%2520factors%2520that%2520could%2520lead%2520to%2520a%2Ccontinued%2520to%2520use%2520abatements%2520using%2520one%252Dtime%2520deals.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebase%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHighsmith%20and%20Manduca%20hope%20their%20research%20can%20push%20policymakers%20to%20consider%20addressing%20the%20advantages%20and%20disadvantages%20caused%20by%20fragmentation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20a%20version%20of%20this%20effort%20to%20address%20fragmentation%20was%20taking%20place%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20which%20is%20among%20the%20most%20fragmented%20states%20in%20the%20country.%20Particularly%20relaxed%20incorporation%20laws%20have%20caused%20New%20Jersey%20to%20be%20dotted%20with%20dozens%20of%20odd%20tiny%20municipalities%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bdonut%20hole%26quot%3B%20towns%2C%20where%20one%20town%20is%20entirely%20surrounded%20by%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGina%20Genevese%2C%20a%20tennis%20pro%20turned%20Mayor%20of%20New%20Jersey's%20Longhill%20Township%2C%20created%20the%20nonprofit%20Courage%20to%20Connect%20NJ%20in%202009%2C%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20consolidating%20some%20of%20these%20towns.%20It%20was%20an%20effort%20that%20had%20some%20success%2C%20Genevese%20says%2C%20but%20it%20also%20faced%20tremendous%20backlash%20from%20entrenched%20interests%20who%20benefited%20from%20the%20additional%20government%20jobs%20created%20by%20multiple%20small%20towns%2C%20along%20with%20prosperous%20towns%20who%20hoped%20to%20keep%20their%20tax%20wealth%20to%20themselves.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20want%20to%20share%2C%26quot%3B%20Genevese%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20push%2C%20Teterboro%20found%20itself%20in%20the%20crosshairs%20once%20again.%20In%202010%2C%20then%20State%20Senator%20Bob%20Gordon%20put%20forward%20a%20bill%20to%20dissolve%20the%20town%2C%20which%20he%20describes%20as%20the%20%26quot%3BCayman%20Islands%20of%20New%20Jersey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20huge%20tax%20base%20that%20is%20just%20sitting%20there%20exclusively%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20people%20that%20own%20the%20real%20estate%20in%20Teterboro%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Gordon.%20His%20plan%20was%20the%20same%20as%20Albanese's%20back%20in%20the%201960s%20%E2%80%94%20divide%20the%20town's%20property%20tax%20wealth%20among%20the%20surrounding%20communities.%20The%20move%20was%20projected%20to%20provide%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20in%20annual%20property%20tax%20relief%20to%20homeowners%20in%20surrounding%20towns%2C%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20like%20walking%20into%20a%20buzzsaw%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20didn't%20appreciate%20is%20that%20there%20were%20some%20very%20powerful%20interests%20quite%20satisfied%20with%20the%20status%20quo.%26quot%3B%20While%20there%20were%20no%20accusations%20of%20threats%20or%20bribery%20this%20time%2C%20Teterboro%20business%20interests%20lined%20up%20against%20the%20move%2C%20launching%20a%20lobbying%20campaign.%20Teterboro%20residents%20voted%20against%20dissolution%2020-1%20in%20a%202010%20referendum%2C%20and%20the%20bill%20died%20in%20the%20legislature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20certainly%20against%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Saros%2C%20Teterboro's%20municipal%20manager.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20business%20owners%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we%20have%20big%20corporate%20owners%20here%20%E2%80%94%20would%20say%2C%20'that%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20sense%2C%20my%20tax%20rate%20will%20go%20up.'%20I%20mean%2C%20who%20would%20want%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fguthrie-scrimgeour%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EGuthrie%20Scrimgeour%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20an%20investigative%20journalist%20based%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20covering%20wealth%20and%20power.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftax-haven-usa-mapping-tiny-tax-shelters-scattered-across-america-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772702221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8b2601fb3fcb42648f0e7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftax-haven-usa-mapping-tiny-tax-shelters-scattered-across-america-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Inside%20500%20American%20towns%20where%20the%20rich%20shelter%20their%20money.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Guthrie%20Scrimgeour)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftax-haven-usa-mapping-tiny-tax-shelters-scattered-across-america-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20company%20behind%20Cinnabon%20can%20conquer%20the%20Ozempic%20era%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22746%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20row%20of%20Cinnabon%20cinnamon%20rolls%20with%20toppings%20including%20pecans%20and%20Oreo%20cookies.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a77d1dd3e2f1aef369f039%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22419%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGoTo%20Foods'%20new%20CEO%20says%20the%20company%2C%20parent%20of%20brands%20like%20Cinnabon%2C%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20Ozempic%20era%20with%20wellness-focused%20menu%20innovations.%3Cp%3EGoTo%20Foods%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAs%20more%20consumers%20turn%20to%20GLP-1%20medications%2C%20food%20and%20restaurant%20brands%20are%20redefining%20themselves.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGoTo%20Foods'%20CEO%20says%20the%20company%20is%20ready%20for%20its%20Ozempic%20era%20with%20wellness-focused%20menu%20tweaks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrands%20like%20Cinnabon%20and%20Jamba%20will%20see%20coming%20changes%20focused%20on%20small%20portions%20and%20other%20benefits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20era%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feli-lillys-orforglipron-beats-novo-nordisk-glp1-pill-in-tests-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eappetite-suppressing%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20brands%20like%20Cinnabon%2C%20Jamba%2C%20and%20McAlister's%20Deli%20says%20it's%20built%20to%20handle%20changing%20cravings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%20trend%20really%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoto-foods-new-ceo-omer-gajial-food-court-cinnabon-jamba-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoTo%20Foods%20CEO%20Omer%20Gajial%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider%2C%20noting%20that%20GLP-1%20use%20is%20expected%20to%20expand%20dramatically%20over%20the%20next%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGajial%20sees%20opportunity%20for%20innovation%20across%20even%20GoTo%20Foods'%20most%20indulgent%20brands%20as%20the%20use%20of%20weight-loss%20drugs%20expands%20and%20consumers%20increasingly%20prioritize%20protein%2C%20fiber%2C%20and%20digestive%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it's%20tough%20to%20apply%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployers-cutting-back-employee-wellness-benefits-fitness-money-gyms-healthcare-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewellness%20lens%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20sweet-treat%20icons%20like%20Cinnabon%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20just%20because%20of%20their%20decadent%20recipes.%20Recent%20research%20from%20the%20consumer%20insights%20firm%20Curion%20suggests%20that%20overt%20GLP-1%20branding%20could%20backfire%20due%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BGLP-1%20Menu%20Paradox%26quot%3B%3A%20more%20than%20half%20of%20consumers%20say%20they%20would%20likely%20order%20smaller%2C%20protein-forward%20versions%20of%20popular%20menu%20items%20if%20offered%2C%20yet%20over%20a%20third%20actively%20reject%20anything%20labeled%20%26quot%3BGLP-1-friendly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStaying%20the%20course%20isn't%20an%20option%2C%20as%20there's%20a%20financial%20cliff%20awaiting%20brands%20that%20fail%20to%20respond%20to%20changing%20consumer%20habits.%20And%20nearly%20a%20quarter%20of%20current%20GLP-1%20users%20surveyed%20by%20Curion%20said%20they%20regularly%20order%20from%20the%20kids'%20menu%20as%20a%20workaround%20for%20smaller%20portions%2C%20which%20is%20a%20big%20blow%20toward%20already%20razor-thin%20margins%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20costs%20are%20up%2C%20and%20consumer%20spending%20is%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20explicit%20GLP-1%20labeling%2C%20demand%20is%20rising%20among%20both%20medication%20users%20and%20the%20broader%20public%20for%20flexible%20portion%20sizes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-new-protein-cold-foams-taste-test-better-than-expected-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprotein-first%20framing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20smaller%20indulgent%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20GLP-1%20has%20done%20is%20bring%20those%20needs%20into%20sharper%20focus%2C%26quot%3B%20Rachel%20Buss%2C%20vice%20president%20of%20strategic%20insights%20at%20Curion%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20about%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20firm's%20findings.%20%26quot%3BThe%20same%20menu%20architecture%20that%20works%20for%20a%20GLP-1%20user%20also%20works%20for%20the%20macro-tracker%2C%20the%20runner%2C%20the%20fitness-focused%20consumer.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20niche%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20mainstream.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f0f9847-ae73-4ea2-9633-539142e94460%5C%22%3EGoTo%20Foods%20is%20thinking%20similarly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20radically%20reinventing%20menus%2C%20Gajial%20described%20the%20company's%20focus%20as%20%26quot%3Belevating%20the%20benefits%20that%20already%20exist%26quot%3B%20on%20its%20menus.%20At%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-jim-holthouser-ceo-goto-foods-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMoe's%20Southwest%20Grill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20for%20example%2C%20customers%20were%20already%20adding%20double%20protein%20to%20bowls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20we%20had%20to%20do%20was%20to%20rearrange%20and%20say%2C%20'This%20has%2068%20grams%20of%20protein%20in%20a%20bowl%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20ingredients%20were%20there%3B%20it%20was%20the%20positioning%20that%20shifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPortion%20flexibility%20is%20another%20lever%20that%20will%20be%20adjusted%20across%20the%20GoTo%20Foods%20portfolio.%20Gajial%20acknowledged%20that%20some%20customers%20now%20prefer%20smaller%20servings%20due%20to%20satiety%20changes%20caused%20by%20the%20use%20of%20GLP%20drugs.%20In%20response%2C%20the%20company%20has%20introduced%20bite-sized%20options%2C%20including%20a%20new%20%26quot%3Bdippers%26quot%3B%20product%20at%20Moe's%20featuring%20two%20smaller%20burritos%20paired%20with%20sauce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20brands%20%E2%80%94%20from%20Cinnabon%20to%20its%20sandwich%20concepts%20%E2%80%94%20Gajial%20said%20GoTo%20is%20working%20to%20%26quot%3Boffer%20customers%20choice%26quot%3B%20so%20they%20can%20select%20%26quot%3Ba%20smaller%20serving%20solution%20that%20meets%20their%20needs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20approach%20aligns%20closely%20with%20Curion's%20recommendations%20for%20operators%3A%20focus%20on%20%26quot%3Bportion%20architecture%2C%26quot%3B%20prioritizing%20protein%20content%20over%20calorie%20counts%2C%20and%20offering%20smaller%20versions%20of%20menu%20staples%20to%20give%20consumers%20choice%20without%20complicating%20delivery%20logistics%20or%20workflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoTo's%20portfolio%2C%20which%20includes%20restaurant%20concepts%20as%20well%20as%20food%20court%20staple%20brands%2C%20gives%20it%20multiple%20angles%20to%20consider.%20Gajial%20said%20further%20details%20of%20its%20updated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaco-bell-gen-z-appeal-strategy-culturally-relevant-ceo-says-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emenu%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%20would%20be%20unveiled%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20and%20pointed%20to%20Jamba%20in%20particular%20as%20having%20%26quot%3Bstretchability%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20capable%20of%20operating%20both%20as%20a%20specialty%20snack%20brand%20and%20a%20restaurant%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20emphasized%20that%2C%20by%20building%20smaller%20formats%2C%20highlighting%20protein%2C%20and%20letting%20customers%20choose%20without%20labeling%20them%2C%20the%20company%20behind%20some%20of%20America's%20most%20recognizable%20mall%20treats%20is%20redefining%20itself%20for%20what%20Buss%20calls%20%26quot%3Bappetite%20economics%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20a%20world%20where%20not%20just%20what%20people%20eat%2C%20but%20how%20much%20they%20eat%2C%20is%20fundamentally%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcinnabon-jamba-parent-company-ready-ozempic-wellness-era-menu-innovation-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772702041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a77d38fd4fbd083f2978ea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcinnabon-jamba-parent-company-ready-ozempic-wellness-era-menu-innovation-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22GoTo%20Foods'%20new%20CEO%20says%20the%20company%2C%20parent%20of%20brands%20like%20Cinnabon%2C%20is%20ready%20for%20the%20Ozempic%20era%20with%20wellness-focused%20menu%20innovations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ktl%40businessinsider.com%20(Katherine%20Tangalakis-Lippert)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcinnabon-jamba-parent-company-ready-ozempic-wellness-era-menu-innovation-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title