C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20trade%20groups%20are%20pressing%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20his%20administration%20to%20quickly%20pay%20tariff%20refunds%20to%20small%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20press%20release%2C%20the%20Consumer%20Technology%20Association%20and%20the%20US%20Chamber%20of%20Commerce%20said%20they%20had%20filed%20a%20brief%20on%20Wednesday%20in%20V.O.S.%20Selections%2C%20Inc.%20v.%20Trump%2C%20a%20lawsuit%20by%20small%20businesses%20seeking%20refunds%20from%20Trump's%20sweeping%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20brief%20argues%20that%20an%20efficient%2C%20orderly%20process%20to%20deliver%20refunds%20is%20in%20the%20best%20interest%20of%20all%20parties%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Administration%2C%20the%E2%80%AFcourts%2C%E2%80%AFand%20American%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20behalf%20of%20the%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20businesses%2C%20especially%20small%20businesses%2C%20that%20are%20now%20owed%20refunds%2C%20the%20Chamber%20and%20CTA%20are%20asking%20the%20court%20to%E2%80%AFestablish%E2%80%AFan%20efficient%2C%20orderly%20process%20to%20deliver%20refunds%3Cem%3E%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fem%3Een%E2%80%AFmasse%2C%26quot%3B%20Neil%20Bradley%2C%20the%20Chamber's%20executive%20vice%E2%80%AFpresident%2C%E2%80%AF%20said%20in%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20trade%20organizations%20were%20concerned%20that%20other%20parties%20might%20try%20to%20benefit%20from%20the%20refund%20process%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bthe%20last%20thing%20our%20system%20needs%20is%20for%20the%20trial%20bar%20to%20be%20profiting%20off%20refunds%20owed%20to%20small%20businesses.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20matters%20for%20every%20American%20company%2C%20refunds%20are%20existential%20for%20the%20many%20smaller%20businesses%20and%20startups%20who%20shouldered%20the%20tariff%20burden%2C%26quot%3B%20Ed%20Brzytwa%2C%20CTA's%20vice%20president%20of%20international%20affairs%2C%20said%20in%20the%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trade%20groups'%20filing%20comes%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsupreme-court-scotus-rules-trump-tariffs-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%20ruled%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%206-3%20decision%20in%20February%2C%20that%20Trump's%20tariffs%20were%20illegal%20and%20that%20his%20justification%20for%20invoking%20the%20International%20Emergency%20Economic%20Powers%20Act%20was%20invalid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-refunds-ieepa-judge-clears-path-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJudge%20Richard%20K.%20Eaton%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20US%20Court%20of%20International%20Trade%20ruled%20that%20US%20businesses%20that%20were%20subjected%20to%20tariffs%20are%20%26quot%3Bentitled%20to%20the%20benefit%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20Eaton's%20ruling%2C%20companies%20had%20started%20demanding%20refunds.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthere-top-global-companies-have-sued-trump-for-tariff-refunds-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMajor%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Costco%2C%20Toyota%2C%20BYD%2C%20and%20FedEx%20filed%20lawsuits%20against%20the%20administration%2C%20seeking%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20tariff%20duties%20since%20they%20were%20imposed%20last%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20the%20Trump%20administration%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-trade-groups-pressing-trump-tariff-refunds-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1772696436000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a920461fb3fcb42648f379%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus