20leaving%2C%20urging%20them%20to%20evacuate%20by%20commercial%20means.%20The%20embassy%20in%20Jerusalem%20said%20in%20a%20notice%20on%20Tuesday%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20US%20Embassy%20is%20not%20in%20a%20position%E2%80%AFat%20this%20time%E2%80%AFto%20evacuate%20or%20directly%20assist%20Americans%20in%E2%80%AFdeparting%E2%80%AFIsrael.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20they%20are%20now%20issuing%20notices%20telling%20Americans%20that%20government%20assistance%20is%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20X%20post%20late%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20State%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20a%20Department%20of%20State%20charter%20flight%20of%20American%20citizens%20departed%20the%20Middle%20East%20in%20route%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20as%20part%20of%20our%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20assist%20Americans%20return%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22twitter%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EToday%2C%20a%20Department%20of%20State%20charter%20flight%20of%20American%20citizens%20departed%20the%20Middle%20East%20in%20route%20to%20the%20United%20States%2C%20as%20part%20of%20our%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20assist%20Americans%20return%20home.Additional%20flights%20will%20be%20surged%20across%20the%20region%20and%20American%20citizens%20in%20UAE%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Saudi%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4egntuuWy3%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F4egntuuWy3%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Department%20of%20State%20(%40StateDept)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FStateDept%2Fstatus%2F2029354917471678936%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%205%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Badditional%20flights%20will%20be%20surged%20across%20the%20region.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20did%20not%20say%20which%20Middle%20Eastern%20country%20the%20charter%20flight%20on%20Wednesday%20had%20departed%20from.%20The%20State%20Department%20post%20included%20photos%20showing%20consular%20staff%20standing%20next%20to%20US%20Embassy%20banners%20at%20an%20airport%2C%20with%20the%20country's%20name%20blurred%20on%20the%20signage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20embassy%20in%20Jerusalem%20said%20in%20a%20late%20Wednesday%20notice%20that%20the%20US%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Bready%20to%20help%20Americans%20leave%20the%20Middle%20East%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20the%20options%20available.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20security%20alert%20by%20the%20US%20embassy%20in%20Kuwait%20communicated%20the%20same%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20notice%2C%20the%20embassy%20added%20a%20link%20to%20a%20crisis%20intake%20form%2C%20which%20included%20the%20option%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20seeking%20U.S.%20government%20departure%20assistance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20embassy%20in%20Riyadh%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20said%20in%20an%20X%20post%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20%26quot%3BAmericans%20trying%20to%20get%20home%20from%20Israel%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20or%20Qatar%2C%26quot%3B%20should%20fill%20out%20the%20crisis%20intake%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Wednesday%20notice%20from%20the%20embassy%20in%20Doha%2C%20Qatar%2C%20however%2C%20said%20it's%20%26quot%3Bcurrently%20exploring%20options%20to%20assist%20U.S.%20citizens%20in%20reaching%20a%20safe%20destination%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20did%20not%20provide%20a%20link%20to%20the%20crisis%20intake%20form.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20Americans%20in%20the%20following%20countries%20should%20vacate%3A%20Bahrain%2C%20Egypt%2C%20Iran%2C%20Iraq%2C%20Israel%2C%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Gaza%2C%20Jordan%2C%20Kuwait%2C%20Lebanon%2C%20Oman%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Syria%2C