llion%20investment%20in%20OpenAI%20is%20'probably%20not%20in%20the%20cards'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223343%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jensen%20Huang%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a8ee971fb3fcb42648f297%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222229%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJensen%20Huang%20says%20a%20%24100%20billion%20OpenAI%20investment%20is%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20not%20in%20the%20cards%2C%26quot%3B%20citing%20the%20AI%20startup's%20move%20toward%20an%20IPO.%3Cp%3EHarun%20Ozalp%2FAnadolu%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20%24100%20billion%20investment%20in%20OpenAI%20is%20unlikely%2C%20says%20Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20go%20public%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20at%20a%20conference.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20finalized%20our%20agreement.%20We're%20going%20to%20invest%20%2430%20billion%20in%20OpenAl%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20says%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20%24100%20billion%20investment%20in%20OpenAI%20is%20likely%20off%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20at%20a%20Morgan%20Stanley%20conference%20in%20San%20Francisco%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20such%20a%20massive%20investment%20in%20the%20ChatGPT%20maker%20is%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20not%20in%20the%20cards%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20going%20to%20go%20public%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20for%20everybody's%20update%2C%20we%20finalized%20our%20agreement.%20We're%20going%20to%20invest%20%2430%20billion%20in%20OpenAl%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20might%20be%20the%20last%20time%20we'll%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20consequential%20company%20like%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Nvidia%20said%20it%20could%20invest%20up%20to%20%24100%20billion%20in%20OpenAI%20as%20part%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-investing-up-to-100-billion-openai-ai-deal-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20partnership%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20build%20out%20AI%20infrastructure.%20The%20deal%20would%20see%20the%20companies%20construct%20%26quot%3Bat%20least%2010%20gigawatts%26quot%3B%20of%20AI%20data%20centers%20powered%20by%20Nvidia%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Nvidia%20will%20focus%20on%20supplying%20the%20massive%20computing%20power%20OpenAI%20needs%20to%20train%20and%20run%20its%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20revenues%20will%20more%20than%20follow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20Nvidia's%20%2410%20billion%20investment%20in%20OpenAI%20rival%20Anthropic%20%26quot%3Bprobably%20will%20be%20the%20last%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%2C%20the%20maker%20of%20Claude%2C%20is%20preparing%20to%20go%20public%2C%20and%20investor%20demand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-spvs-shares-investor-interest-grows-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efor%20its%20shares%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20rising%2C%20Joseph%20Alagna%2C%20founding%20partner%20of%20Buttonwood%20Funds%2C%20one%20of%20Anthropic's%20largest%20shareholders%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang's%20comments%20follow%20speculation%20last%20month%20that%20there%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-jensen-huang-oracle-tension-billion-dollar-deal-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epotential%20tensions%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20multibillion-dollar%20investment%20in%20OpenAI.%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20reported%20that%20some%20Nvidia%20executives%20had%20raised%20internal%20concerns%20about%20the%20deal%2C%20citing%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20Taipei%20in%20February%2C%20Huang%20dismissed%20the%20suggestion%20that%20he%20was%20unhappy%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bnonsense.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20he%20strongly%20supports%20the%20startup's%20work%20and%20Altman's%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20in%20OpenAI.%20The%20work%20that%20they%20do%20is%20incredible%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Nvidia%20would%20%26quot%3Binvest%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20money%2C%20probably%20the%20largest%20investment%20we've%20ever%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20has%20also%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20on%20CNBC's%20%26quot%3BMad%20Money%26quot%3B%20last%20month%20that%20he%20would%20welcome%20the%20chance%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20future%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-nvidia-back-future-openai-ipo-sam-altman-drama-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20among%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20privately%20held%20AI%20companies%20and%20a%20key%20customer%20for%20Nvidia's%20chips%2C%20which%20are%20used%20to%20train%20and%20run%20large%20language%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20has%20not%20publicly%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20go%20public%2C%20but%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20capital%20and%20computing%20power%20needed%20to%20develop%20advanced%20AI%20systems%20has%20prompted%20speculation%20about%20how%20it%20will%20fund%20its%20next%20phase%20of%20expansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20January%20exchange%20on%20Substack%2C%20%26quot%3BBig%20Short%26quot%3B%20investor%20Michael%20Burry%20said%20he%20was%20struck%20by%20how%20ChatGPT%20had%20%26quot%3Bkicked%20off%20a%20multi-trillion-dollar%20infrastructure%20race.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20someone%20built%20a%20prototype%20robot%20and%20every%20business%20in%20the%20world%20started%20investing%20for%20a%20robot%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C