%3Cp%3EOctober%20soil%2C%20cooled%20after%20the%20monsoon%2C%20welcomes%20new%20seedlings.%20Marigolds%20thrive%20in%20this%20transition%2C%20soaking%20up%20the%20mellow%20sunlight%20and%20rewarding%20patient%20gardeners%20with%20blooms%20that%20last%20through%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENature%E2%80%99s%20protector%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20without%20formal%20horticulture%20training%2C%20grandmothers%20knew%20marigolds%20had%20quiet%20powers.%20They%20repel%20pests%20like%20nematodes%20and%20aphids%2C%20protecting%20vegetables%20and%20other%20flowers%20nearby.%20Farmers%20still%20border%20fields%20with%20marigold%20rows%20for%20the%20same%20reason.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20small%20home%20gardens%2C%20a%20corner%20of%20marigolds%20acted%20as%20a%20natural%20shield%2C%20keeping%20soil%20healthy%20and%20guarding%20against%20tiny%20invaders%20long%20before%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98organic%E2%80%99%20became%20fashionable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EGolden%20memories%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMarigolds%20also%20evoke%20afternoons%20of%20stringing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F465241%2Fwest-bengal-dropout-marigold-farming-success-business-earning-crores-arup-ghosh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflowers%20into%20garlands%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20fingers%20sticky%20with%20their%20citrusy%20fragrance.%20Grandmothers%20patiently%20taught%20children%20how%20to%20knot%20each%20bloom%20together%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20lessons%20in%20gardening%2C%20but%20in%20patience%2C%20craft%2C%20and%20continuity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-31T222111.433-1756659080.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bright%2C%20v