rl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Floods%20Ravage%20Punjab%2C%203.5%20Lakh%20Struggle%20To%20Survive.%20Be%20Their%20Lifeline%2C%20Donate%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mohan%20Singh%20was%20preparing%20to%20harvest%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekharif%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecrops%20on%20his%20field%20this%20week.%20He%20was%20elated%3B%20it%20had%20been%20a%20great%20season.%20So%20picture%20his%20devastation%20when%20he%20walked%20out%20onto%20his%20field%20three%20days%20ago%2C%20and%20saw%20that%20the%20green%20had%20been%20replaced%20by%20steadily%20rising%20water.%20Mohan%20belongs%20to%20Gurdaspur%20in%20Punjab%2C%20which%20is%20inundated%20by%20the%20waters%20flooding%20the%20state.%20The%20relentless%20heavy%20rains%20are%20compounded%20by%20the%20dangerously%20high%20levels%20of%20the%20Sutlej%2C%20Beas%2C%20and%20Ravi%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20is%20drowning.%20It%20needs%20your%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDONATE%20NOW%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDonate%20to%20help%20Punjab%20flood%20victims%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mohan%2C%20like%20the%203%2C54%2C000%20people%20(as%20of%205%20September)%20affected%2C%20did%20not%20have%20time%20to%20grieve.%20His%20only%20priority%20was%20ensuring%20that%20his%20family%20made%20it%20out%20of%20the%20house%20alive.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20escape%3B%20the%20only%20option%20was%20to%20wait%20and%20pray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496899%7D%5C%22%20h